'''''A Bug's Life: An Original Walt Disney Records Soundtrack''''' is the original soundtrack album to ''A Bug's Life'', produced by [[Walt Disney Records]]. The album was released on October 27, 1998.<ref name="apple1">{{cite web|url=https://itunes.apple.com/us/album/bugs-life-original-walt-disney/id156087339 |title=iTunes - Music - A Bug's Life (An Original Walt Disney Records Soundtrack) by Randy Newman |publisher=Itunes.apple.com |date=2001-10-23 |accessdate=2013-10-21}}</ref> The album's first track is a song called "The Time of Your Life" written and performed by Newman, while all the other tracks are orchestral cues.<ref name="apple1"/> The album has gone off the market but is available for purchase on [[iTunes]].<ref name="apple1"/>

The score won the [[Grammy Award]] for [[Grammy Award for Best Score Soundtrack for Visual Media|Best Instrumental Composition]].<ref name="apple1"/>
 
